---
/*
 * PullQuote.astro — an emphasised pull-quote that animates in on scroll.
 *
 * Breaks the wall-of-text with a large, accent-bordered line. Reveals via [data-reveal]
 * (motion.js); reduced-motion users see it immediately. RU-first: put RU in the slot.
 *
 * USAGE:
 *   <PullQuote>Высокий APY — это не приз, это <strong>вопрос</strong>: «за какой риск мне платят?».</PullQuote>
 */
---
<blockquote class="ac-pullquote" data-reveal>
  <slot />
</blockquote>
